author: Animalogic
description:
The vaquita is the most critically endangered marine mammal. Overfishing, criminal groups, and poor management had led them to the brink of extinction. But after decades of failed conservation efforts, we finally have a plan to save them. These are the people protecting the world's rarest whale.
